Total cost of studying MBBS in Ukraine

Ukrainian is one of the preferred destinations to study MBBS because of the quality education being provided by highly experienced and qualified faculty. Ukraine medical university fees is economical for students who want to study MBBS. The total cost of studying MBBS in Ukraine is much cheaper than Indian medical colleges.

MBBS fees in Ukraine universities/colleges would range anywhere between 15 to 25 lacs. The course duration for pursuing MBBS in Ukraine is 6 years which includes a one-year internship program. The students can do medicinal practice in India or abroad after completing the MBBS course from the MCI approved top medical universities in Ukraine.
